message: /* Location */ Location is still the same

/* Subsidiary companies */ `There has been a great change in the company from the last time our Wiki page was published. This has been in term of products we currently have in our catalogues, expansion of the company services, change in management and amalgamation of all the different companies to one - Mukwano Industries Uganda Limited.
Tony Gadhoke is the Chief Executive Officer of Mukwano not the Managing Director.
Tony Gadhoke is actually the Chief Executive Officer of Mukwano Industries Uganda Limited not the Managing Director.
